<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Shifting sand and wind deflation are the primary disturbance agents, and <i>Pleuraphis rigida</i> serves as stabilizer over wide areas of sand. Fire effects are not well known. Open stands are less likely to carry fire than are those on rocky substrates. Some recently burned upland stands appear affected while other stands have expanded (Matthews 2000b).</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
